{"tid":2206348,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"楊潤雄：來自中央的壓力是最少","createTime":"2020-09-17T12:09:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-17T16:30:03.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"eda1dc555086d30f380bb4b067fcfa18d2529451","tid":2206348,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T12:09:57.000Z","msg":"多間出版社早前參與教育局的通識科教材專業諮詢計劃後，刪去或修改「三權分立」內容，教育局局長楊潤雄接受本台節目《議事論事》訪問，表示教科書要就是非對錯提供正確資料，不能有含糊的地方。<br />\n<br />\n楊潤雄說，有評論曾質疑是否每名教師都完全認識「三權分立」及帶動學生討論，他說不會低估教師的能力，但質疑是否每名教師都能做到，因此認為在中小學階段先教導一些事實和基礎較實際。<br />\n<br />\n被問到提出修改是否源自一些壓力，楊潤雄強調自己一直面對議員、社會和一些意見領袖等多方面的壓力，但來自中央的壓力是最少。他說，希望修改後的內容配合課程宗旨，內容要準確，避免只有一面倒的意見或在概念上模糊不清。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1550220-20200917.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1550220-20200917.htm&d=sV3HumZuViP2rFeoL7TNOO9tl09raJ%2B2zMWOssuGUT0%3D&h=aa14f2d8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1550220-20200917.htm&h=01257a76\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1550220-20200917.htm</a>"},{"pid":"db939a356e4984a8a0689e132f99464bb48ff911","tid":2206348,"uid":201359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T12:10:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a25568a0b27a8b46a8318abe31e18f0c76a8f37","tid":2206348,"uid":274532,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T12:10:41.000Z","msg":"就是非對錯提供正確資料，不能有含糊的地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b2e3899b2bb114ccf064c0d5242bc143c6e49d3","tid":2206348,"uid":54511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020